# Task 8 – Interface Design

## Sports Hall Booking System using ServiceNow Service Portal

### Overview

This task focuses on designing the user interface (UI) for the Sports Hall Booking System using the ServiceNow Service Portal. The objective is to provide a clean, responsive, and user-friendly interface that enables users to easily browse sports facilities, check slot availability, and submit booking requests.

---

## Objective

Design an intuitive and responsive Service Portal interface that enhances user experience and simplifies the sports hall booking process.

---

## Features Implemented

- Responsive Service Portal Homepage
- Navigation Menu
- Sports Hall Listing
- Available Slot Display
- Booking Request Form
- Booking Confirmation Page
- User Dashboard
- My Bookings Page
- Profile Section

---

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow Service Portal
- HTML
- CSS
- Bootstrap
- AngularJS
- JavaScript

---

## Interface Components

### Home Page
- Welcome Banner
- Sports Categories
- Quick Booking Button
- Announcements Section

### Sports Hall Page
- Hall Name
- Description
- Capacity
- Available Slots
- Book Now Button

### Booking Form
- User Details
- Sports Type
- Booking Date
- Time Slot
- Number of Players
- Remarks

### Dashboard
- Current Bookings
- Booking Status
- Booking History

---

## UI Design Principles

- Responsive Layout
- Simple Navigation
- Clean Design
- Consistent Color Scheme
- Easy Accessibility
- Mobile Friendly

---

## Expected Outcome

Users can easily:

- View available sports halls
- Check slot availability
- Submit booking requests
- Track booking status
- Access their booking history

---

## Deliverables

- Responsive Interface Design
- Service Portal Pages
- Booking Form UI
- Dashboard Layout
- User-Friendly Experience

---

